/// This software can't be used to automate games. Games often protect themselves from being automated, for example by disabling artificial clicks, keystrokes and hotkeys.

/// Keyboard and mouse functions can't be used to automate a background window while another window is active. A workaround could be to run the script and the target software on a <google>virtual machine</google>. Some functions can automate some background windows, for example <see cref="elm.Invoke"/>, other <see cref="elm"/> functions, <see cref="mouse.postClick"/>.
